1. Authenticate

Send a POST to get an auth token:

curl -k -X POST "https://<flash500-ip>/REST/auth" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"username":"superuser","password":"yourpassword"}'


The response will include an X-Auth-Token.

2. Trigger Support Package Creation
curl -k -X POST "https://<flash500-ip>/REST/systems/1/support_packages" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-H "X-Auth-Token: <your_token>" \
-d '{"type":"full"}'


type can be "full" or "minimal".

Response includes an id for the support package.

3. Download the Support Package
curl -k -X GET "https://<flash500-ip>/REST/systems/1/support_packages/<package_id>/file" \
-H "X-Auth-Token: <your_token>" \
-o support_package.tgz
